# The merge driver is registered globally in the codeflare container image
# (AD52). The `binary` attribute is a defensive fallback for clones outside
# that image: git falls back to a binary "take one side" merge instead of
# attempting a textual 3-way merge on the 155k-line generated JSON.
# Either way the file is regenerable via `graphify update .` after a conflict.
graphify-out/graph.json merge=graphify binary
